metadata.name: Peaceful Warrior
metadata.description:
Life can be seen as strings tightly woven which each strand, connects everything in the fabric of life.
Humans, like the strings of a carpet beautifully placed by each other in different colors and patterns as to form a country.
Truly should these strings come apart, nothing would remain of the beauty and the carpet, just like people being devided and no form of correlation remains to stabilize the nation
.
.
Acrylic on Canvas.
Neo-expressionism 
40×50 Cm
4236×3412
.
HadisKhaefi 2022
